304
00:15:13,146 --> 00:15:15,081
‐ <i>What's the squirt packing?</i>

305
00:15:15,148 --> 00:15:19,019
‐ Believe it or not,
the Czech vz. 61, two of 'em.

306
00:15:20,721 --> 00:15:23,123
