307
00:15:23,189 --> 00:15:24,791
‐ And with its pink outfit,

308
00:15:24,858 --> 00:15:28,328
you won't even know it's there
'til you hear its guns.

309
00:15:31,131 --> 00:15:32,933
‐ <i>It'll ventilate you</i>
<i>before you even</i>

310
00:15:32,999 --> 00:15:35,468
