311
00:15:39,640 --> 00:15:41,207
‐ [gasps]

312
00:15:41,274 --> 00:15:43,577
‐ You're even teenier
than the rumors say.

313
00:15:43,644 --> 00:15:46,279
Nice to meet you, Pink Devil.

314
00:15:46,346 --> 00:15:48,448
I guess you got
so used to beating everyone

315
00:15:48,515 --> 00:15:50,751
that came out here,
you let your guard down.

316
00:15:50,817 --> 00:15:52,886
Are you having fun killing?

317
00:15:52,953 --> 00:15:56,156
I mean, it is "GGO."
It's just a game,

318
00:15:56,222 --> 00:15:58,925
and what's wrong
with killing people in a game?

319
00:15:58,992 --> 00:16:00,994
There's nothing wrong with that.

320
00:16:01,061 --> 00:16:02,362
Even so...

321
00:16:02,428 --> 00:16:04,565
‐ [gasps]

322
00:16:05,599 --> 00:16:08,201
‐ never let your guard down
in here.

323
00:16:08,268 --> 00:16:10,937
‐ Wait. What?
Aren't you gonna shoot me?

324
00:16:11,004 --> 00:16:12,739
‐ Of course not.

325
00:16:12,806 --> 00:16:16,042
I was just curious
what this Pink Devil was like,

326
00:16:16,109 --> 00:16:17,944
so I came to see for myself.

327
00:16:18,011 --> 00:16:19,212
I never expected you'd be

328
00:16:19,279 --> 00:16:21,915
this teeny‐tiny
cutesy‐wootsy girl, though.

329
00:16:21,982 --> 00:16:24,484
Hey, what do you say
we go back to town

330
00:16:24,551 --> 00:16:25,385
and have some drinks?

331
00:16:25,451 --> 00:16:27,253
Let your Big Sis here treat you.

332
00:16:27,320 --> 00:16:29,790
There aren't that many
female players around here,

333
00:16:29,856 --> 00:16:31,658
so we might as well be friends.

334
00:16:31,725 --> 00:16:33,994
Karen: <i>And that's how</i>
<i>I met this strange woman</i>

335
00:16:34,060 --> 00:16:37,197
<i>named Pitohui,</i>
<i>or Pito for short.</i>

336
00:16:38,699 --> 00:16:39,800
‐ Ooh!

337
00:16:39,866 --> 00:16:42,669
So that's how you keep
on the down‐low in town.

338
00:16:42,736 --> 00:16:44,337
So sneaky.

339
00:16:44,404 --> 00:16:46,472
Anyway, time for introductions.

340
00:16:46,540 --> 00:16:50,644
My name is Pitohui,
or just Pito for short.

341
00:16:50,711 --> 00:16:52,813
And you? What's your name.

342
00:16:52,879 --> 00:16:54,815
‐ [gasps] Nice to meet you.

343
00:16:54,881 --> 00:16:56,382
I'm LLENN. That's it.

344
00:16:56,449 --> 00:16:59,753
‐ No way? "LLENN"?
That's the cutest name ever.

345
00:16:59,820 --> 00:17:01,855
And relax. I won't bite you.

346
00:17:01,922 --> 00:17:02,856
‐ Ohh.
‐ What?

347
00:17:02,923 --> 00:17:04,791
Are my tats freaking you out?

348
00:17:04,858 --> 00:17:06,226
‐ No, not at all.

349
00:17:06,292 --> 00:17:08,929
‐ It's okay. Like I said,
girls are rare here,

350
00:17:08,995 --> 00:17:10,463
so I was always getting hit on,

351
00:17:10,531 --> 00:17:13,433
but once I got my tats,
the creepers left me alone.

352
00:17:13,499 --> 00:17:15,268
Maybe you should
get some yourself.

353
00:17:15,335 --> 00:17:17,671
‐ No, thanks!
Pitohui, have you‐‐

354
00:17:17,738 --> 00:17:19,472
‐ Just Pito is fine.

355
00:17:19,540 --> 00:17:21,074
‐ O‐Okay, Pito.

356
00:17:21,141 --> 00:17:24,044
Have you been playing VR games
a long time now?

357
00:17:24,110 --> 00:17:26,112
‐ Yeah. You could say that.

358
00:17:26,179 --> 00:17:29,616
I've been playing "GGO" since
the very first day it came out.

359
00:17:29,683 --> 00:17:33,654
It's got a bloodthirsty vibe you
won't find in other VR games.

360
00:17:34,955 --> 00:17:36,356
How long have you been playing?

361
00:17:36,422 --> 00:17:38,124
‐ This is the first one.

362
00:17:38,191 --> 00:17:40,226
I started about
three months ago, actually.

363
00:17:40,293 --> 00:17:41,695
‐ No way. You're just a noob?

364
00:17:41,762 --> 00:17:43,564
Sneaking up on people
and murdering 'em

365
00:17:43,630 --> 00:17:45,832
left and right
like you do takes talent.

366
00:17:45,899 --> 00:17:47,167
You vicious little thing!

367
00:17:47,233 --> 00:17:49,870
‐ Maybe I should dial
the murdering back a bit.

368
00:17:49,936 --> 00:17:52,472
‐ Not even. Hey, I know.

369
00:17:52,539 --> 00:17:54,174
Let's register as friends.

370
00:17:54,240 --> 00:17:56,142
I can teach you a lot
about this game.

371
00:17:56,209 --> 00:17:58,845
Besides, I'm sick
of playing with sleazy guys.

372
00:17:58,912 --> 00:18:00,514
Come on. What do you say?

373
00:18:00,581 --> 00:18:01,515
‐ Okay.

374
00:18:03,383 --> 00:18:05,318
And that takes care of that.

375
00:18:05,385 --> 00:18:07,287
We're gonna have fun
playing together.

376
00:18:07,353 --> 00:18:08,488
‐ Yep!
‐ [sighs]

377
00:18:08,555 --> 00:18:10,657
I didn't realize it was so late.

378
00:18:10,724 --> 00:18:12,058
You gonna log off?

379
00:18:12,125 --> 00:18:13,927
‐ I wanted to go and check out

380
00:18:13,994 --> 00:18:15,461
some live‐ammo guns
before I did.

381
00:18:15,529 --> 00:18:18,231
‐ Heck, I know
the best place in town.

382
00:18:18,298 --> 00:18:22,335
