and the toughest monsters.

385
00:18:27,073 --> 00:18:28,742
LLENN: Wow!

386
00:18:30,611 --> 00:18:32,045
Amazing.

387
00:18:32,112 --> 00:18:34,648
This place has everything.

388
00:18:34,715 --> 00:18:35,916
‐ LLENN, over here.

389
00:18:35,982 --> 00:18:37,551
This looks right up your alley.

390
00:18:37,618 --> 00:18:39,653
It says
