391
00:18:40,954 --> 00:18:42,222
Check it out.

392
00:18:43,123 --> 00:18:45,391
‐ What is that?

393
00:18:48,261 --> 00:18:50,997
Gosh, that's cute.

394
00:18:51,064 --> 00:18:52,866
It's just darlin'!

395
00:18:52,933 --> 00:18:55,669
‐ Someone sounds
like they're from Hokkaido.

396
00:18:55,736 --> 00:18:57,938
‐ I want it. I need it.

397
00:18:58,004 --> 00:19:00,707
I gotta have it!

398
00:19:02,976 --> 00:19:04,511
‐ I know that feeling.

399
00:19:04,578 --> 00:19:06,212
There's nothing
like walking home

400
00:19:06,279 --> 00:19:07,681
