401
00:19:07,748 --> 00:19:10,551
You wanna get used
to how she handles.

402
00:19:10,617 --> 00:19:12,118
‐ Yup.

403
00:19:12,185 --> 00:19:14,454
‐ Now that she's yours,
she needs a name.

404
00:19:14,521 --> 00:19:17,123
‐ A‐Am I supposed
to give my gun a name?

405
00:19:17,190 --> 00:19:18,291
‐ Yeah, of course.

406
00:19:18,358 --> 00:19:20,426
‐ I wonder what to call her.

407
00:19:21,528 --> 00:19:22,362
I know!

408
00:19:22,428 --> 00:19:24,565
‐ I hope it's cool. Well?

409
00:19:24,631 --> 00:19:26,533
