410
00:19:27,433 --> 00:19:28,835
‐ She's P‐chan.

411
00:19:28,902 --> 00:19:30,103
‐ Perfect.

412
00:19:30,170 --> 00:19:31,304
Yeah, it fits.

413
00:19:31,371 --> 00:19:33,206
