<i>as a two‐person squad.</i>

421
00:19:51,792 --> 00:19:54,327
<i>Whenever we were online</i>
<i>at the same time,</i>

422
00:19:54,394 --> 00:19:56,797
<i>we'd hang out</i>
<i>or go hunting together.</i>

423
00:19:56,863 --> 00:19:59,700
<i>I never saw her</i>
<i>use the same weapon twice,</i>

424
00:19:59,766 --> 00:20:02,035
<i>so I figured</i>
<i>she was super rich.</i>

425
00:20:02,102 --> 00:20:05,238
<i>Other than that, I didn't</i>
<i>really know much about her.</i>

426
00:20:05,305 --> 00:20:07,674
‐ [yawns]
