427
00:20:07,741 --> 00:20:09,976
‐ Huh? Mm...

428
00:20:10,043 --> 00:20:11,612
other than playing "GGO"?

429
00:20:11,678 --> 00:20:12,513
Nothing, really.

430
00:20:12,579 --> 00:20:14,748
‐ Well, I like
listening to music.

431
00:20:14,815 --> 00:20:17,884
I'm really into stuff
like classical and soundtracks.

432
00:20:17,951 --> 00:20:21,287
As for pop singers,
Elza Kanzaki's my favorite now.

433
00:20:21,354 --> 00:20:23,123
‐ Music's your thing, huh?

434
00:20:23,189 --> 00:20:25,659
