about real life in here.

441
00:20:39,072 --> 00:20:42,142
‐ No, it's okay. We know
each other pretty well by now.

442
00:20:42,208 --> 00:20:44,745
I mean, at this point,
I don't see what harm it'd do

443
00:20:44,811 --> 00:20:47,180
