anywhere you want.

456
00:21:19,546 --> 00:21:22,048
‐ A‐Are you kidding me?

457
00:21:22,115 --> 00:21:23,617
Okay, you got a deal!

458
00:21:23,684 --> 00:21:26,252
One of these days, me and
P‐chan will take you down.

459
00:21:26,319 --> 00:21:28,889
‐ Sweet.
